{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act42side", "eventName": "眾生行記", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "MT-4", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "求道", "storyInfo": "能天使發現育嬰聖堂住滿了無辜的難民，她不得不拆除自己的炸彈，並意外遇到了前來調查的蕾繆安。與此同時，費德里科找到了阿爾圖羅，但二人似乎都注意到了拉特蘭的異樣。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g2_laterano_cathedralhall", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tech_intro", "key": "$tech_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您為什麼要用這樣彆扭的姿勢靠牆站著？我還以為自己看見了一尊雕像……", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#4$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你要是早一點進來，就能聽見我的關節發出喀喀的聲音了，哈哈。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來得抽空去找一下工匠師傅，看能不能在腰間加裝一塊護枕……", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "銃騎裝甲的設計師大概不會考慮這種關愛老年人的特殊設計……", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這主要是為了緩衝巨銃後座力嘛，年輕的銃騎也需要！", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明天降生儀式就要開始了，育嬰聖堂那邊準備得怎麼樣了？", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位母親的狀態很穩定，安多恩將她照顧得相當好，相信明天她會誕下一位健康且美麗的新生兒。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維什戴爾議長和卡茲戴爾使節團、雙子女皇和萊塔尼亞使節團、阿戈爾發展規劃所執政官代表團、炎國宣禮使帶領的天師團……", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明天，所有到訪聖城的客人都會受邀前往育嬰聖堂，共同見證那個新生命的降生。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，既然一切正常，你今天找我是為了什麼？", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的新人樞機……", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安？", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她專程去見了一趟牧首。我想——", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她應該不是在調查爆炸事件時“偶然”經過，“順便”看看，再“心血來潮”地提出以第七廳的名義為育嬰聖堂提供幫助吧？", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我起初以為她是為安多恩遇襲的事來的。但她見過牧首之後的表現……很明顯她還有更多疑慮。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還以為我已經打消了她的疑慮。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安的敏銳很多時候無人能及，尤其在她注意某件事的時候。我很想說，她確實就是最適合成為七廳樞機的那個人。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#7$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她同時也是不適合的。畢竟，她的注意力在哪，似乎大部分時候只取決於她自己的私人判斷。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#2$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈。那你覺得有必要對她加以防範嗎？", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……您這個語氣，搞得好像我們是什麼反派，正在醞釀顛覆拉特蘭的大陰謀一樣。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難說喲。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對於有些人來說，我們將要迎接的那個未來，恐怕確實會顛覆他們所知的生活。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的共感，我們的同胞與親族，甚至“薩科塔”這個概念本身……都將拋卻舊有的局限。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這本來是拉特蘭所行之道既定的終點，但這道路畢竟綿延了太長、太久。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許有些人反倒將過程中伴生的一些微不足道的意外現象當作了常態，以至於無法接受原本既定的終點。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說得也是。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#11$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們還是應該早點做好準備。", "name": "薇爾麗芙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1780_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安的事情，我會處理。你就回到育嬰聖堂，專心準備明天的儀式吧。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "願主繼續賜福這座城。", "name": "帕特里奇昂"}, "figure_art": "avg_4194_rmixer_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g4_nurseryindoor", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$ponder_intro", "key": "$ponder_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_comfortbell", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.5, "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "頭髮火紅的薩科塔在蒼白與幽藍交織的叢林中東奔西走，像一撮小小的火苗在雨中搖曳。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#10$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個安撫鈴上的雲朵都快比可頌的麵包車大了……還有那個能塞下兩個貨櫃的搖籃……", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_comfortbell", "volume": 1.0, "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.5, "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "安撫鈴上懸掛的雲朵彷彿能遮蔽天光，托舉搖籃的雙手似乎又要聳入雲霄。"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這座聖堂之中，一切活物都顯得渺小。"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "能天使"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會……", "name": "能天使"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g3_nurserytemplecorridor", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#11$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來空蕩蕩的，安靜得要死，但這些育嬰室，起碼有一半以上都住了人……", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小孩子、異族人甚至還有墮天使……保育員忙來忙去，看樣子他們應該已經住進來很久了。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那群人不是說這裡大部分的設施都還不能使用，要等到那個什麼儀式辦完之後才開放嗎？", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "完全不是這麼回事！", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-20", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行……得拆掉這些炸彈！", "name": "能天使"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#11$1", "posfrom": "0,-20", "posto": "0,-20", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "本來以為先把場地炸掉，儀式就無法順利舉辦了，結果這裡面全都是人……", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真要命啊，好不容易才躲開那些守衛安裝好的……", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tidyequipment", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#10$1", "posfrom": "0,-20", "posto": "0,-20", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……要是她們在就好了。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可以拜託德克薩斯把守衛全部打暈拖到外面去，或者讓可頌撞開那些房間，把裡面的人統統打包帶走……", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#5$1", "posfrom": "0,-20", "posto": "0,-20", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實在不行，這群人舉辦儀式的時候，就讓老闆在對面開一個粉絲見面會之類的，把注意力都吸引過去……", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#5$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tidyequipment", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#10$1", "posfrom": "0,-20", "posto": "0,-20", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，繼續，沒剩多少時間了。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拆掉這些炸彈，再想別的辦法——", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#10$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先剪掉那根藍色的線，拆起來會比較快哦。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 5.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#6$1", "posfrom": "0,-20", "posto": "0,-20", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔啊……", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你什麼時候回來的？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小樂。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "26_g10_laterano_roof", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這棟住宅很普通，唯一的特點是天台的視野——剛好可以看清育嬰聖堂前的廣場。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿爾圖羅，這是你選擇躲藏在此的原因？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又見面了呢。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你找了過來，而且速度比想像中快了很多。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#2$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你並沒有想要隱藏自己的行跡。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你用紙蜻蜓脫身，留下了太過明顯的線索。在崔林特爾梅的時候，我不只一次見過你使用類似的音樂術式。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，雖然很不願意承認……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你真的掌握了我的許多秘密，費迪。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，你們……", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#10$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "席德佳修女，難道我們的執行者先生沒有告訴你，我是他的姐姐嗎？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#12$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#10$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你我的遠親關係，並不妨礙我作為執行者對你實施監視與管控。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿爾圖羅，將你帶回拉特蘭之前，在崔林特爾梅的城外，我曾向你提出警告——", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會對你保持更高的警惕，審慎判斷你行為的主觀動機與可能導致的客觀結果。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果發現任何可疑的地方，我會擊斃你。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還記得那天的晚霞。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#11$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "席德佳修女，他真的是一個刻板到有趣的人，對吧？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#12$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿爾圖羅小姐，一直以來，您都非常配合我們的安排。所以受監管期間，蘭登修道院並沒有太為難您。", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您欺騙了我們！", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我深表歉意，席德佳修女。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#2$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希望我的無禮行為不會給你、給蘭登修道院帶來不好的影響。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#6$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿爾圖羅，交代你擅自離開蘭登修道院的目的。", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看這座聖堂，費迪。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#2$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多麼雄偉且富有生命力的建築，它聳入雲端，高度甚至遠遠超過了萊塔尼亞人引以為傲的女皇雙塔……", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#4$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是拉特蘭試圖為自己打造的“恩典”與“權威”？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#3$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看看那些正被引入其中的、沒有光環的異族人。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉特蘭需要他們做什麼？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#9$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿爾圖羅，你究竟發現了什麼？", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回到拉特蘭前，我們曾在羅德島短暫停留，還記得嗎？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#4$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在那裡見到了一位神秘的客人。他告訴我，或許終有一日，拉特蘭將不再是專屬於薩科塔們的溫馨小屋。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#4$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費迪，還有席德佳修女，看看眼前的景象，你們難道不曾懷疑，這一天已經到來了嗎？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們引以為傲的聖城，為何變了模樣？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#8$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1784_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是，什、什麼意思？", "name": "席德佳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1784_1#10$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "費德里科"}, "figure_art": "avg_1032_excu2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "費迪，從來都清醒的你，顯然也察覺到了什麼，不是嗎？", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "否則，在見到我的第一秒，你就已經舉起了銃。", "name": "阿爾圖羅"}, "figure_art": "avg_245_cello_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g3_nurserytemplecorridor", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些是，炸彈？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#6$2"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來威力還不小。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老姐，你的腿已經完全恢復了？！", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯啊。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "太好了！", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小樂，我那天在約維塔街看到的，以及阿摩斯輔佐官在銃械工坊外看到的，都是你嗎？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#14$2"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "教皇廳已經對爆炸物進行了相當嚴苛的管控，竟然還能做出這麼多炸彈……小樂，你這方面的本事還是那麼好。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿嘿。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#5$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，小樂，你的目的是什麼？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#5$2"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "炸毀這座聖堂？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#5$2"}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阻止降生儀式？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#5$2"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是，破壞整個萬國峰會？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#5$2"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別過來，老姐。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "61_i07", "block": "false", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 65.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巨型立柱切割開了光影，蕾繆安停下腳步，沒有繼續走向能天使。"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老姐，你這一套是樞機的制服吧？", "name": "能天使"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好看嗎？", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很合身！超級帥氣！", "name": "能天使"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其實稍微有一點大，上任前一天剛領到，我還連夜自己動手改了一下腰線呢。", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，真不希望久別重逢是在穿著這套制服的場合。", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小樂是一個人回來的嗎？還是說有其他朋友陪著你，他們也在附近？", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，老姐你在套我的話耶！", "name": "能天使"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小樂是個想法單純的孩子嘛。這不是學校，也不是畢業典禮，小樂真的只是心血來潮想要用這樣的方式助興嗎？", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是誰在你身後，又為什麼將你推到這個位置？", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我……", "name": "能天使"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿——口令，“美乃滋蘋果派”！", "name": "能天使"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "口令，“烤一塊吃一塊”。", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊！小時候的事情，老姐你竟然還記得！", "name": "能天使"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要遇到吵不出結果的架，不願意說的秘密，就快點喊口令暫停，把矛盾存起來。", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小樂，姐姐能感受到你的情緒，糾結、急切、焦慮，甚至不知道該從哪裡開始解釋……", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但將試圖破壞萬國峰會的危險分子捉拿歸案，這是姐姐的職責所在。我也會向教皇廳申請親自負責本案的後續審理。", "name": "蕾繆安"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "薩科塔姐妹對峙著，兩個人沒有挪動腳步，也沒有再說一句話。終於，蕾繆安忍不住打破了沉默，她長長地嘆了一口氣。"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉~", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.4, "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0, "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "61_g3_nurserytemplecorridor", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幾乎是在同一個瞬間，能天使撲了過來，將她抱緊。"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#3$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$2", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這才是你每次闖禍後的第一反應啊。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#11$2"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真想你啊，老姐！", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼久沒見，你好像長高了一點？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈哈哪有！我離開拉特蘭的時候都快成年了好嗎！", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老姐你這個口吻，就像那種很愛操心的家長的標準語氣。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#9$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈，是這樣嗎？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#9$2"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#6$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個辮子是你自己綁的嗎？都鬆掉了。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#6$2"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我幫你重新綁一下……你還是這樣馬馬虎虎的。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的手藝當然沒有你的好嘛。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老姐，你今天為什麼會來到這裡？總不可能是因為你知道我會出現吧？", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是來確認聖堂的安防……本來以為見到牧首為一位薩卡茲孕婦祈禱就已經夠特別了……", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒想到又碰見了你。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（牧首……薩卡茲孕婦……祈禱……）", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#11$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（難道說，降生儀式就是……）", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，老姐，原來你也不是很清楚這座聖堂裡有什麼嘛！", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 336, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小樂，你不會打算反過來套我的話吧？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這又是誰教你的？", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老姐——我真的沒有跟人學壞啦。現在支持我做這些事的人——我向你保證——是很可靠的！", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有孤軍奮戰，也沒有被人利用哦。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一切都很不對勁，但更詳細的我很難向你說明……我還需要一點時間。", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_1041_angel2_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "做完該做的事情，我會回家的！", "name": "能天使"}, "figure_art": "avg_1041_angel2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#14$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#14$2"}, {"id": 348, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#14$2", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蕾繆安綁好了髮圈的最後一圈，又往上綁緊一點，讓妹妹頭側邊的那束頭髮不至於那麼容易鬆。"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#3$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#3$2", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但下一個瞬間，她的懷抱已經空了。"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#3$2", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剩下的這些炸彈，就麻煩樞機大人幫我拆掉囉！", "name": "能天使"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "炸彈的倒數計時聲在多處同時響起，蕾繆安看著妹妹消失的方向，卻無法繼續追上去。"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……真沒辦法啊。", "name": "蕾繆安"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1811_1#1$2"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}